m/gallery/KMPlbqK</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yml3eWd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Decided to clear out my phone after a few years of hoarding memes and such. I thought it was interesting how the political landscape has changed, so I compiled some of the more relevant ones. I also included some other stuff for levity.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wOqryMM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Covid started when I was still in high school.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WjlBopM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Start by voting. Then as you vote, rally and protest, and if that doesn’t work, strike, and if that doesn’t work, start making molotovs.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wByt67Z.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>No romance or sex, only class consciousness.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/18U4swZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The republican party is a fascist organization. Anyone who says otherwise has been brainwashed.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8dgECu5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Levity.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/R8TjNZ6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>People deserve fair wages.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tYL3HWv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>In order to fight intolerance, a society must itself be intolerant to intolerance.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0iDB9jC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And also conservatives.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/o2tTqOK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Worker exploitation at Amazon fucking sucks.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JUbGOMW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Levity.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4KXKcyo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Equity.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/By6xxIw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This meme format is wrong, but the sentiment rings true.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/F76JC8M.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And now use bastardized christian dogma to try and create a fascist theocracy.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QRaMzGq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Conservatism by nature opposes progress.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vdee4VE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Brainwashing and indoctrination scare the shit out of me.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/loPcpWO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This has been the vibe for a while and I’m sick of it…</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zFgVLty.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The republican party recently decided that the mask was making it hard to breathe, so it’s now going without it.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/msClT8u.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The separation of the church and the state is so fucking important.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/q77Qbdx.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Programs like these are the backbone of a secure society. Any of these being weak severely kneecaps progress.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/k7qUPfv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Seeing this right now. Kill me.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/v6Nrlxi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Fixing this shit is important. Fuck, everything is important.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PinClIZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Conservatives have a tendency to think about an issue for 10 minutes and then decide they’re experts on it and refuse to do any more reading or adjust their position in accordance to factual evidence.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xGV9nDn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I hate this timeline.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SriVWSH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I’ll take the one on the bottom over the one on the top any day of the week. Apathy and abstinence kill progressive momentum.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zEoEppu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The police force needs serious reform and restructuring.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DV0w3kv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The Satanic Temple is the good one, NOT the Church of Satan.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lFyq0h7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We need to teach ethics in school again.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FCeVm8X.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Deregulation in the 80s created a capitalist hellscape. Regulate or riot.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OODgQb8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>See: conservatives who immediately stop shouting “ban abortion” when their 15 year old daughter gets pregnant.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/txS8M6S.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The Trump era isn’t over yet… I want that greasy motherfucker in chains.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IJk3col.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Also applies to social issues.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QvQ1Owr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Levity.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AwX0hwu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Levity… I got pretty depressed for a while.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wNDOslM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Expand the Supreme Court. And add term limits for both it and the senate. Abolish the electoral college.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0zQNydv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Levity. He makes me smile.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lafNqVl.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>As previously stated, in order to protect itself from intolerance, a tolerant society must itself be intolerant to intolerance.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8w3eFLE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>More topical now that it was when I saved this.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MIE3VXB.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>People are dying. And somehow other people don’t care.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tO1rEIs.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Goddamn fucking fascists.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dga2KZR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Fox News should not be able to call itself news.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bBKJ5VD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Abortion rights are human rights. We’ve officially reached the present.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PsEitCT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Trump is thrashing and writhing like a fish on the bank. Put him out of his misery like the fish: bash his skull with a stone.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/h7CWxP6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Love thy neighbor in practice.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gATNzxB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>White nationalists can eat shit.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZZJQR7D.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Religion should never be a relevant factor in politics.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zXFUoNv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Uvalde and the Roe decision have made me angrier than literally anything else in my entire life. I hate feeling angry all the time. It stresses me out, makes me depressed, and leads to apathy. But I can’t be apathetic. Lives and rights are on the line.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KUElcNz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The supreme court is inherently corrupt.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TN09V1H.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Cat tax. He’s fond of laying under or near the plants.

Most Viral Edit: I could use some serotonin today, so if you have a pet, either comment or send me a picture! No nudes please :).</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/KMPlbqK</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[thewitchbasket]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Peperidge Farm remembers.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/AOPwBT8</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/H2zKKzg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/AOPwBT8</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DaShanghaiKid]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>But both sides… right?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Kf2bd5t</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PhWE6Mo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://mobile.twitter.com/dissentingj/status/1541401721079009281</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4vxe0Au.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dkjq7qv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Kf2bd5t</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[license2kilt]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Images of Note: Very over all this shit</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/mjWmBd7</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pPu4xcA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7lwgY6T.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ngzXTep.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sERCGR3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/p9bWAVX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"